        <headline>Heat Advisory issued August 7 at 11:36AM CDT until August 7 at 8:00PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...Hot temperatures up to 105 expected.

* WHERE...Dallam and Hartley Counties.

* WHEN...Until 8 PM CDT this evening.

* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures and high humidity may cause heat
illnesses.
</description>
        <instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
